I see you.

791
00:41:37,940 --> 00:41:39,010
Be careful.

792
00:41:55,890 --> 00:41:56,870
I finally see you.

793
00:41:58,710 --> 00:41:59,740
What's wrong?

794
00:42:06,070 --> 00:42:07,480
How is your mother?

795
00:42:08,490 --> 00:42:09,020
Not bad.

796
00:42:09,510 --> 00:42:10,940
Didn't you say

797
00:42:10,940 --> 00:42:12,140
