Here.

808
00:42:39,870 --> 00:42:40,350
Go back.

809
00:42:41,090 --> 00:42:41,700
Thanks.

810
00:42:41,850 --> 00:42:43,380
You're welcome. Bye.

811
00:42:43,540 --> 00:42:44,300
See you.

812
00:42:54,230 --> 00:42:55,940
Are you okay, Hua Juan?

